>[Thoughts]
>5(a^2-b/a-b)=11(a^2-b/a-b)
>(5a^2-5b)(11a-b)=(11a^2-b)(5a-b)
>55a^3-5a^2b-11ab+b^2=55a^3-11a^2b-5ab+b^2
